summary: 该插件用于检测通天星-CMSV6系统的delete-downloadLogger功能是否存在SQL注入漏洞，通过延迟响应判断漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the delete-downloadLogger function of the Tongtianstar-CMSV6 system has an SQL injection vulnerability, and determines the existence of the vulnerability by judging the delay response.
